<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(كان حيا قبل ١٢٧٥ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">(١٨٥٩ م)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>يوحنا بنيان. فاضل.<span class="c5"> من آثاره:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
